435
01:12:40,640 --> 01:12:41,639
You bitch!

436
01:12:59,520 --> 01:13:01,199
Load the horses.

437
01:13:15,760 --> 01:13:18,399
You've caused enough trouble, bitch.

438
01:13:34,600 --> 01:13:35,919
Kill him.

439
01:13:36,960 --> 01:13:38,359
I love to.

440
01:13:54,240 --> 01:13:55,399
Shit!

441
