444
01:15:47,360 --> 01:15:49,799
Goddamn, shit... I'll get it!

445
01:15:51,480 --> 01:15:52,879
I got it!

446
01:15:54,240 --> 01:15:57,039
I got mine! I got mine!

447
01:16:18,240 --> 01:16:22,999
With the gold, I'll pay me
girls, whiskey...

