On that day in 1880

454
01:19:59,080 --> 01:20:04,039
our tribe was once again saved
from the greed of the white man.

455
01:20:04,200 --> 01:20:06,399
But that day would not last.

456
01:20:06,840 --> 01:20:10,759
For their fever for our
Yellow Rock would not turn.

457
01:20:11,480 --> 01:20:15,079
As my great-grandfather,
Angry Wolf said:

458
01:20:15,240 --> 01:20:17,479
"They will come as drops in water."

459
01:20:17,640 --> 01:20:21,399
"And rain down upon us."

460
01:20:21,560 --> 01:20:23,319
And this they do.

461
01:20:24,640 --> 01:20:27,839
I'm called Black Feather, the Raven,

462
01:20:29,520 --> 01:20:32,159
Omen of death to our people.

